quran[27{c,v,t}:
55,68,Feehimaa faakihatunw wa nakhlunw wa rummaan
55,69,Fabi ayyi aalaaa'i Rabbikumaa tukazzibaan
55,70,Feehinna khairaatun hisaan
55,71,Fabi ayyi aalaaa'i Rabbikumaa tukazzibaan
55,72,Hoorum maqsooraatun fil khiyaam
55,73,Fabi ayyi aalaaa'i Rabbikumaa tukazzibaan
55,74,Lam yatmis hunna insun qablahum wa laa jaaann
55,75,Fabi ayyi aalaaa'i Rabbikumaa tukazzibaan
55,76,Muttaki'eena 'alaa rafratin khudrinw wa 'abqariyyin hisaan
55,77,Fabi ayyi aalaaa'i Rabbikumaa tukazzibaan
55,78,Tabaarakasmu Rabbika Zil-Jalaali wal-Ikraam
56,1,Izaa waqa'atil waaqi'ah
56,2,Laisa liwaq'atihaa kaazibah
56,3,Khafidatur raafi'ah
56,4,Izaa rujjatil ardu rajjaa
56,5,Wa bussatil jibaalu bassaa
56,6,Fakaanat habaaa'am mumbassaa
56,7,Wa kuntum azwaajan salaasah
56,8,Fa as haabul maimanati maaa as haabul maimanah
56,9,Wa as haabul mash'amati maaa as haabul mash'amah
56,10,Wassaabiqoonas saabiqoon
56,11,Ulaaa'ikal muqarraboon
56,12,Fee Jannaatin Na'eem
56,13,Sullatum minal awwaleen
56,14,Wa qaleelum minal aa khireen
56,15,'Alaa sururim mawdoonah
56,16,Muttaki'eena 'alaihaa mutaqabileen
